326	   * elements; otherwise a single-element array `[linkId]` identifying the
327	   * `link_model` row whose source contains the element. (Multi-hop transitive
328	   * links are deferred — the FED-01 expander is single-hop only.)
329	   */
330	  linkChainA?: string[];
331	  linkChainB?: string[];
332	};
